```
$ PATH=$HOME/node_modules/.bin/:$PATH tsc
client.ts:3:16 - error TS2306: File '/home/alex/codaz/Mozilla/DeepSpeech/deepspeech-kdavis/native_client/javascript/index.d.ts' is not a module.

3 import Ds from "./index";
                 ~~~~~~~~~


Found 1 error.
